deficiency_sse21dd: Chord connection plate or arm plate broken or cracked.
deficiency_criteria_sse21dcd: 2 or more nuts in a 4 bolt configuration, OR 2 or more nuts in a 6 bolt configuration, OR 3 or more nuts in an 8 or more bolt configuration
recommendation_sse21rd: Lower structure, retrofit short anchor bolt assembly to restore full capacity, or remove structure.
